# AllSets

# Minor Description

AllSets outputs every set unless flags are used to omit certain sets

# Set

PropertyTypeExampleDescription
baseSetSizeinteger259Number of cards in the set. Note that Wizards sometimes prints extra cards beyond the set size into promos or supplemental products.
blockstring"Guilds of Ravnica"Block the set was in.
boosterV3array(array, string, ...)[["rare", ...], "uncommon", ... ]Contents of a typical booster.
cardsarray(object, ...) [ #{Card}#, ... ] List of cards. See the #{Card}# object.
codestring"RNA"Set code for the set.
codeV3stringAlternate set code Wizards uses for a select few duel deck sets. (If there is not an alternate set code, this field is omitted.)
isFoilOnlybooleanfalseSet available only in foil. (If false, it is usually omitted.)
isOnlineOnlybooleanfalseSet available online only. Can be true or false. (If false, it is usually omitted.)
metaobject(string, string){"date": "#{_Date}#", "version": "${_Version}#"}Keys are date and version. Date (OBDC standard) is date of build. Version is version of MTGJSON release.
mtgoCodestring"RNA"Set code for the set as it appears on Magic: The Gathering Online.
namestring"Ravnica Allegiance"Name of the set.
releaseDatestring"2019-01-25"Date of release for the set.
tcgplayerGroupIdinteger2366Group ID of the set on TCGPlayer.
tokensarray(object, ...)[#{Token}#, ...]List of tokens for the set. See the #{Token}# object.)
totalSetSizeinteger273Total number of cards in the set, including promos and related supplemental products.
typestring"expansion"Type of set. See #{SetTypes}# examples.
